{"tid":1668033,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(迫你買新機)舊款 iPhone‧iPad 隨時失靈！Apple 發布緊急通知！","createTime":"2019-10-21T18:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T07:38:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"512786e964b6f044f8652c41b8ffb529c01a0966","tid":1668033,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:57:03.000Z","msg":"舊款 iPhone‧iPad 用家留意！Apple 官方發布緊急通知，部份舊款 iPhone‧iPad 有機會因以下原因，而引致部份功能失靈，影響時間、日期顯示出錯，甚至是令部份 Apps 無法正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n舊款 iPhone‧iPad 隨時失靈<br />\nApple 發布緊急通知<br />\n更新 iOS 可解決<br />\nApple 官方支援網站發布題為「Update your iPhone or iPad software to avoid issues with location, date, and time」的文章，內文指出部份舊款 iOS 裝置包括 iPhone 5、iPad 4 等等，其 GPS 定位功能存有 Bug，並在 11 月 3 日後有機會出現定位問題，並影響部份需要使用 GPS 的功能，像系統時間日期同步，如裝置時間偏差較大，更會影響 iCloud 及電郵接收，同時也影響部份需要使用 GPS 定位的 Apps。Apple 指受影響的裝置只要更新 iOS 到指定或以上版本，即可解決，詳情見下表。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2475000/2479035/001_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2475000%2F2479035%2F001_600.JPG&h=da69be76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a56ccb7f51344ca792cb4d5e2760c6a8667b9382","tid":1668033,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:59:00.000Z","msg":"update完會正常用到 不過瘋狂燒電咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28f396fc669d1d9208b563954fe608762cdc05b","tid":1668033,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:00:41.000Z","msg":"Chairman cook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ad868dfe473ecc977cf55f83bd8945c5846e61","tid":1668033,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:32:43.000Z","msg":"佢俾佢地上12/13先係新聞"},{"pid":"b8566a411fdb1ae7456fb293dbbc71a5cdc71be5","tid":1668033,"uid":241300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2